*DBD-mysql-4.20.0-r1 (20 Aug 2014)

  20 Aug 2014; Ian Stakenvicius (_AxS_) <axs@gentoo.org>
  +DBD-mysql-4.20.0-r1.ebuild, -DBD-mysql-4.20.0.ebuild:
  bumped EAPI to 5; committed directly to stable as no other changes present and
  revbump helps stable systems to keep from dieing on perl-5.18 upgrade

  05 Sep 2013; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> -DBD-mysql-4.01.7.ebuild:
  drop old

  05 Sep 2013; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> DBD-mysql-4.20.0.ebuild:
  Mark s390/sh stable #478748.

